==Japanese version==
There's a choco pie made in Japan (well, at least you can buy it in Japan) by Lotte, which is different from the Korean versions that I've bought in the US (I never eaten a choco pie from Korea). The Japanese version is a &quot;chocolate coated vanilla cream sandwich pie&quot; — it doesnt have marshmallow in it, but it does have brandy in it. Subjectively, I like it better than the Korean choco pie. &amp;ndash; [[User:Ish_ishwar|ishwar]]&amp;nbsp;[[User_talk:Ish_ishwar|&lt;small&gt;(speak)&lt;/small&gt;]] 20:25, 8 March 2008 (UTC)

